icon_note: Chart of keyboard bindings for the video game Conan Exiles. IIRC if you print this graphic at 96dpi, it will overlay a real keyboard very closely. This file was generated using Video Game Keyboard Diagrams by Michael Horvath.
derivative_work: Removed all buttons except the function keys. Increased margins. Added text and logo.
